Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:44.99,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,LEVEL MISTERI, SEMENTARA KESATU
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.99,0:14:49.99,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,ISEKAI NONBIRI NOUKA 2
